---
import Page from '../../../../layouts/Page.astro';
const lang = 'en';
---

<Page title="Digital Sovereignty" lang={lang}>
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 bg-cream">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-xs text-charcoal/60 mb-4">Solutions / Outcome</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl leading-tight text-charcoal mb-8">Digital <em>Sovereignty</em></h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-charcoal/70 max-w-3xl">Control your data, your infrastructure, your digital future.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>Digital sovereignty is more than data residency. It's the ability to control your entire digital ecosystem - from the physical infrastructure to the applications running on it.</p>
        <p>TrueLeap provides the complete stack needed to achieve true digital independence while maintaining interoperability with the global internet.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Page>
